<varlistentry id="options.HonorKDEHints">
	<term>HonorKDEHints</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>AfterStep will honor KDE specific hints set on the client's window. This is mainly used for status bar-type applications. The opposite is NoKDEHints.</para>
		<para>See Also: NoKDEHints.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
